{
  "texts": [
    "This would indicate that Chinese native speakers have a relatively high demand for EFL education.",
    "However, it also means that more research needs to be conducted focusing on speakers of other languages to evaluate the LLMs' effectiveness.Another concern related to sampling is the different ages and education levels of EFL learners.",
    "The participants of these studies can be divided into college and middle school students, and they usually have varying learning abilities, learning motivations, and English levels.",
    "In reviewed articles, most of them are focusing on college education [9][10][11][12][13][14], and only two studied middle students [8,15].",
    "According to these articles, these two groups' reactions to LLMs are different."
  ]
}